  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Acapella and ELTGOL Technique to Promote Airway Clearance in COPD:a Comparative Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Acapella and ELTGOL (Expiration in Lateral Position With Open Glottis)Technique to Promote Airway Clearance in COPD Patients:a Comparative Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
